text: Zennewijnen is a village in the Dutch province of Gelderland. It is a part of the municipality of Tiel, and lies about 3 km south of Tiel. The statistical area "Zennewijnen", which also can include the surrounding countryside, has a population of around 60.Statistics Netherlands (CBS), Statline: Kerncijfers wijken en buurten 2003-2005 .
